{"tid":2390000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女童在高速公路上崩潰大哭！ 爸媽丟包理由曝光：夫妻車上吵架","createTime":"2021-02-01T09:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T09:59:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"362218110d1f144249e4320b36a1dd448530c1b9","tid":2390000,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5432/d5432511.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5432%2Fd5432511.jpg&h=f208aa1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者李振慧／綜合報導 <br />\n<br />\n福建泉州一名女童被丟在高速公路上，警方抵達現場發現她嚇得坐在車道旁大哭，身旁沒有任何大人，只好先帶回警局，父母前來認領時坦承，因為夫妻在車上大吵一架，竟然就把年幼的孩子丟在路上。<br />\n<br />\n泉州高速交警上月24日下午1時接到報案，有民眾開車發現一名約3、4歲的女童被丟棄在高速公路上。報案司機表示，當時有一輛廂型車停在路旁，把孩子放下之後就離開。 <br />\n<br />\n員警趕到現場發現，女童嚇得不停大哭也無法說出爸媽資訊，所以先帶回警局安撫，還幫她準備礦泉水、食物與衣服，後來終於查到車輛資訊，將父母傳喚到警局領人。 <br />\n<br />\n自稱是父親的男子下午來到警局，稱因為和妻子吵架才會把女兒丟在路上，由於他無法提供戶籍相關資料，警方只能先將案件交由當地派出所處理，後來證實的確是女童父母，接受批評教育後已和女童一起回家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210201/1911623.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20210201%2F1911623.htm&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=6527c769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210201/1911623.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9756e936778d9279a13c81267238232be69ad048","tid":2390000,"uid":134119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"接受批評教育?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb74d52d195eace479dde2290c5bfd3f79825fd","tid":2390000,"uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:22:22.000Z","msg":"稱因為和妻子吵架才會把女兒丟在路上<br />\n<br />\n唔想嘥錢養女?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a053463621eaafaeaa19b70591b37876e8ad853a","tid":2390000,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e8b3e20de3199daa7bc8bb08dd0a50b7955d07","tid":2390000,"uid":137569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"福建佬唔出奇<br />\n覺得個女係蝕本貨<br />\n睇下仔會唔會咁"},{"pid":"f1bb0c0945d4cb3aa16c17627cce9f33e7221557","tid":2390000,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9756e936778d9279a13c81267238232be69ad048","tid":2390000,"uid":134119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"接受批評教育?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:23:23.000Z","msg":"聽落去有少少似警司警誡就咁鬧你兩句就算"},{"pid":"4f9bbbd905d236ec3cc97c4769ad2a0a0cf5b83c","tid":2390000,"uid":91454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:34:55.000Z","msg":"唔似強國喎<br />\n強國劇本應該係個女仔之後比人話帶佢去搵老豆老母呃左上車<br />\n比人毒啞左之後開始行乞<br />\n8歲開始做雞23－30歲變老雞再比人賣到山區做老婆從此成生育工具+性奴"},{"pid":"dd4f9647fcf5bcdc3591ba74a4d71e8b9b244fdf","tid":2390000,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:36:36.000Z","msg":"要劏雞啦<br />\n冇俾人拐左去"},{"pid":"1e06bbda887f1f14001a868a7468952a69d4cb75","tid":2390000,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:50:24.000Z","msg":"糞斥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187d88f5cb0ddec8c333928fb1857eca09b3d626","tid":2390000,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"可能仔就唔會<br />\n女應該係故意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}